# .skill-description-allowlist — skills permitted to exceed the 250-char
# description ceiling per [SKILL-CREATE-013a].
#
# One skill name per line. # introduces a comment.
#
# Each entry MUST be justified by routing logic that genuinely requires
# longer text (e.g., explicit TRIGGER/SKIP rubrics for SDK disambiguation).
# Architectural enumeration and feature lists do NOT justify allowlisting —
# tighten the description instead.
#
# Reviewed during each cluster review per [SKILL-LIFE-030].

